    "The Firefly dataset is a large-scale collection encompassing 23 Chinese NLP tasks.",
    "It includes tasks related to Chinese culture such as couplet creation, poetry composition, Jin Yong's novels, prose, and more.",
    "Each task is meticulously curated with a variety of manually crafted instruction templates, complemented by additional category labels.",
    "The dataset boasts a substantial scale, amounting to 1.6M instances.",
    "• LIMA-sft (Zhou et al, 2023a)."
